function info($str) { echo "INFO: $str\n"; }
function warn($str) { echo "WARNING: $str\n"; }
function err($str) { die("FATAL ERROR: $str\n"); }

@set_time_limit(0);

@header('Content-Type: text/plain');

chdir(__DIR__);
if (trim(@file_get_contents('.version.php')) !== '<?php // Revision 1266') {
	err('This update can only be applied to OIDplus version 2.0.0.1266!');
}

if (version_compare(PHP_VERSION, '7.0.0') < 0) {
	err('You need PHP Version 7.0 to update to this version');
}

// File added: .idea/misc.xml
function writefile_1() {

	@fwrite($fp, base64_decode('cCI+DQogICAgICA8bWFwPg0KICAgICAgICA8ZW50cnkga2V5PSIkUFJPSkVDVF9ESVIkIj4NCiAgICAgICAgICA8dmFsdWU+DQogICAgICAgICAgICA8U3ZuQnJhbmNoQ29uZmlndXJhdGlvbiAvPg0KICAgICAgICAgIDwvdmFsdWU+DQogICAgICAgIDwvZW50cnk+'));

if (is_file('.idea/misc.xml') && (sha1_file('.idea/misc.xml') != '0b7deeed4a5129995e1e5846cc1e25d2c0a34ee4')) {
	warn('File was created by someone else. Will overwrite the changes now: .idea/misc.xml');
	$tmp = pathinfo('.idea/misc.xml');
	$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('.idea/misc.xml')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
	warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
	if (!@copy('.idea/misc.xml', $backup_name)) {
		warn('Creation of backup failed');
	}
}
writefile_1();
if (!is_file('.idea/misc.xml')) {
	warn('File cannot be created (not existing): .idea/misc.xml');
} else if (sha1_file('.idea/misc.xml') != '0b7deeed4a5129995e1e5846cc1e25d2c0a34ee4') {
	warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): .idea/misc.xml');
} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('.idea/misc.xml', 0644)) {
	warn('Could not change file permissions of .idea/misc.xml');
}

// Dir added: dev/logger
@mkdir('dev/logger');
if (!is_dir('dev/logger')) {
	warn('Directory could not be created: dev/logger');
} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('dev/logger', 0755)) {
	warn('Could not change directory permissions of dev/logger');
}

if (!is_file('.idea/workspace.xml')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: .idea/workspace.xml');
	writefile_3();
	if (!is_file('.idea/workspace.xml')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): .idea/workspace.xml');
	} else if (sha1_file('.idea/workspace.xml') != '3c303395d8d924c3914e7545b37e25c249810b55') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): .idea/workspace.xml');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('.idea/workspace.xml', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of .idea/workspace.xml');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('.idea/workspace.xml') !== '3c303395d8d924c3914e7545b37e25c249810b55') {
		if (@sha1_file('.idea/workspace.xml') !== 'ac991f769b94c7f3745b3984fc863560d0402d3f') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: .idea/workspace.xml');
			$tmp = pathinfo('.idea/workspace.xml');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('.idea/workspace.xml')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('.idea/workspace.xml', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_3();
		if (@sha1_file('.idea/workspace.xml') !== '3c303395d8d924c3914e7545b37e25c249810b55') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): .idea/workspace.xml');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('doc/developer_notes/logger_maskcodes.md')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: doc/developer_notes/logger_maskcodes.md');
	writefile_4();
	if (!is_file('doc/developer_notes/logger_maskcodes.md')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): doc/developer_notes/logger_maskcodes.md');
	} else if (sha1_file('doc/developer_notes/logger_maskcodes.md') != '7f9252f010b7a66335b73d61216497739e7a5536') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): doc/developer_notes/logger_maskcodes.md');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('doc/developer_notes/logger_maskcodes.md', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of doc/developer_notes/logger_maskcodes.md');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('doc/developer_notes/logger_maskcodes.md') !== '7f9252f010b7a66335b73d61216497739e7a5536') {
		if (@sha1_file('doc/developer_notes/logger_maskcodes.md') !== '67899f72acd4ae18a8a5d3237f0b9d9d18bf3869') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: doc/developer_notes/logger_maskcodes.md');
			$tmp = pathinfo('doc/developer_notes/logger_maskcodes.md');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('doc/developer_notes/logger_maskcodes.md')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('doc/developer_notes/logger_maskcodes.md', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_4();
		if (@sha1_file('doc/developer_notes/logger_maskcodes.md') !== '7f9252f010b7a66335b73d61216497739e7a5536') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): doc/developer_notes/logger_maskcodes.md');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
	writefile_5();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php') != 'ebcc54443dc0bc65076674ae3042a0dac1963abc') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php') !== 'ebcc54443dc0bc65076674ae3042a0dac1963abc') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php') !== 'bf81e614a07051f3a38316febf93f8f45990d8b8') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_5();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php') !== 'ebcc54443dc0bc65076674ae3042a0dac1963abc') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplus.class.php');
		}
	}
}

	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: includes/classes/OIDplusAuthUtils.class.php');
	writefile_6();
	if (!is_file('includes/classes/OIDplusAuthUtils.class.php')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): includes/classes/OIDplusAuthUtils.class.php');
	} else if (sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusAuthUtils.class.php') != 'e1b147bc432c3b30e2080022189bd0620c13ee67') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusAuthUtils.class.php');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('includes/classes/OIDplusAuthUtils.class.php', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of includes/classes/OIDplusAuthUtils.class.php');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusAuthUtils.class.php') !== 'e1b147bc432c3b30e2080022189bd0620c13ee67') {
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusAuthUtils.class.php') !== '63f5a641f9a96a4d62f8f01398cb6f51a88419e3') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: includes/classes/OIDplusAuthUtils.class.php');
			$tmp = pathinfo('includes/classes/OIDplusAuthUtils.class.php');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('includes/classes/OIDplusAuthUtils.class.php')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('includes/classes/OIDplusAuthUtils.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_6();
		if (@sha1_file('includes/classes/OIDplusAuthUtils.class.php') !== 'e1b147bc432c3b30e2080022189bd0620c13ee67') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): includes/classes/OIDplusAuthUtils.class.php');
		}
	}

			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/130_create_ra/OIDplusPageAdminCreateRa.class.php', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_10();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/130_create_ra/OIDplusPageAdminCreateRa.class.php') !== '86abded0ae6af4ac19d5c65404be994398af842c') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/adminPages/130_create_ra/OIDplusPageAdminCreateRa.class.php');
		}
	}
}

if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')) {
	warn('File has vanished! Will re-create it: plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	writefile_13();
	if (!is_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')) {
		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	} else if (sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') != '3547a02f2013bcb7c9f779ab1da3170ece590f8b') {
		warn('File cannot be created (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	} else if ((DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR === '/') && !@chmod('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml', 0644)) {
		warn('Could not change file permissions of plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
	}
} else {
	if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== '3547a02f2013bcb7c9f779ab1da3170ece590f8b') {
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== '15eb3636d2e42abcaecef609706b23be602d5c48') {
			warn('File was modified. Will overwrite the changes now: plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
			$tmp = pathinfo('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
			$backup_name = $tmp['dirname'].DIRECTORY_SEPARATOR.$tmp['filename'].'.'.date('Ymdhis',@filemtime('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml')).(isset($tmp['extension']) ? '.'.$tmp['extension'] : '');
			warn('Creating a backup as '.$backup_name);
			if (!@copy('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml', $backup_name)) {
				warn('Creation of backup failed');
			}
		}
		writefile_13();
		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml') !== '3547a02f2013bcb7c9f779ab1da3170ece590f8b') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/language/dede/messages.xml');
		}
	}
}

		if (@sha1_file('plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/820_login_facebook/oauth.php') !== '65aed98d816c40a35862b78dbb3e42f5ef36f748') {
			warn('File cannot be written (checksum mismatch): plugins/viathinksoft/publicPages/820_login_facebook/oauth.php');
		}
	}
}

		warn('File cannot be created (not existing): plugins/viathinksoft/raPages/102_change_email/OIDplusPageRaChangeEMail.class.php');

	}
